00:00:20.059 --> 00:00:24.650
Technological breakthroughs have brought
a revolution in the way we live

00:00:24.650 --> 00:00:27.760
the way we think...

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:31.240
Nowadays communication is solo
accessible

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:32.550
and instant

