00:01:35.009 --> 00:01:37.240
Choose your favorite hero

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:41.760
and customize him as you progress.

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:44.830
ANIMUS offers multiple game modes:

00:01:44.830 --> 00:01:48.020
such as domination and Wolfpack

00:01:48.020 --> 00:01:49.030
domination is a 

00:01:49.030 --> 00:01:54.420
4 versus 4 4 team base mode, where each
team needs to attack

00:01:54.420 --> 00:01:58.799
